"to use for that DM’s statistics (Table 2.5). When DMs enter play, roll "
"1d10. The DM appears in the matching red-numbered hex on the scenario "
"map. When that DM is first encountered, its weakness is determined by "
"rolling a die and consulting the Doomsday Machine Weakness Table (2.6)."
msgstr ""

