msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:2643
msgid ""
"Replicator Flagship and Exploration ships are always faceup. All other "
"Replicator ships remain facedown until revealed. When facedown, they "
"represent Hulls and are not assigned actual ships until revealed."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:2644
msgid ""
"When a Replicator ship (except the Flagship and Exploration ships) enters"
" a Replicator Colony hex, it is flipped facedown and converts back to "
"Hulls, even if its move does not end in that hex. This applies even to "
"Colonies that have been just started. The Replicators can destroy a fleet"
" and a Colony, immediately colonize that planet, and then convert back to"
" Hulls."
msgstr ""

