msgid ""
"• If after the battle, AP ships remain or retreated, their CP value is "
"added back to Fleet Budget and the ships are removed from the board. They"
" are never part of a Fleet."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4901
msgid "AP in Battle"
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4903
msgid ""
"• NPA battles never alter the Paranoia track and never cause a Paranoia "
