msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4904
msgid ""
"• “Off Camera” NPA Battles: As an optional rule, battles between Unknown "
"AP Fleets and NPAs can be resolved with one roll, without generating the "
"AP Fleet. Thus, keeping the Players blind to the contents of that fleet "
"and speeding up the game. This ignores Fleet Strategy. This is done using"
" the table below by finding the line corresponding to the number of NPA "
"counters and the CP value of this Unknown AP Fleet. AP Fleets only attack"
" NPA planets if they have 60 or more CP but lines are included in the "
"table to account for situations in which the AP may unwillingly fight the"
" NPA (i.e. due to card effects). Procedure:"
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4905
msgid "- Draw NPA counters as usual but they will remain face-down."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4906
msgid ""
"- Find the row that matches this fleet’s CP and the column that matches "
"the number of NPA counters in the battle. The intersection is the number "
"needed to roll for the AP to win and the number in parenthesis is the CP "
"lost on a win."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4907
msgid ""
"- Roll a d10. If less than or equal to the listed target value, the AP "
"wins. Some combinations are automatic (i.e. the 10s). Subtract 1 from the"
" target value if the Unknown AP Fleet is Green experience."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4908
msgid "- On a win:"
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4909
msgid "▪ Remove all NPA counters."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4910
msgid ""
"▪ Subtract the lower of: the number in parenthesis or half of this "
"Fleet’s CP (rounded down), from this Fleet’s allocated CP."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4911
msgid ""
"▪ Immediately place a colony ship on the planet and deduct the "
"appropriate amount of CP from Fleet Budget. This is canceled if "
"Terraforming 1 is not researched.."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4912
msgid ""
"▪ If using Crew Experience, roll 1d10. On a 1, this Fleet is promoted. "
"Whether the AP used Ground Troops or had a Colony Ship standing by, you "
"cannot tell."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4913
msgid "- On a loss:"
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4914
msgid "▪ Retreat this Fleet to the safest possible hex."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4915
msgid ""
"▪ If, prior to the battle, the AP Fleet had 40 CP or less, do not remove "
"any NPA counters. If the AP Fleet had 40-59 CP, remove 2 NPA counters. "
"Otherwise, remove 3 NPA counters."
msgstr ""

#: app/data/solo_scenario_book.py:4916
